@node "Document_6" "History"

History
~~~~~~~

1.0 - 14.08.94
      Initial Release

1.1 - Internal Revision

1.2 - 06.02.95
      When the ChatReason was > 70 chars, E!-Page hung. Fixed.

2.0 - 06.07.95
      Completly rewritten to C
      ACP-Page is no longer limited to E! BBS
      Due to this reason it got renamed from E!-Page to ACP-Page.
      Now supports gtlayout.library
      Exchangeable ANSI-Animation.
      Added a .guide Version
@endnode

